fernland
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:land covered, or once covered, with fern, mainly <i>Pteridium esculentum</i> or <i>Paesia scaberula</i>.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: See also <i>fern country</i>. Compare bush-land.
